File Counter (2016 Jan 26)"
recursive file counter that counts files from given directories, excluding the directories itself

usage:	countf.sh [arguments] [file ..]		Counts files recursively in listed files
   or: 	countf.sh 				Counts files recursively from current directory
Arguments:
	 -h		Print help and exit

